Package: agentkit-totp
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: mitchdenny <mitch@mitchdenny.com>
Description: TOTP secret management for AI agents and humans
 A command-line tool for managing TOTP secrets, built with
 .NET NativeAOT for fast startup and minimal dependencies.
 Supports adding, generating, listing, removing and exporting
 TOTP entries with AES-GCM encrypted local storage.
